nfo","message":"Thank you for your report.\n\nHow would an attacker get the link you are using in your example in order to alter this setting for another user?  The IDs used in that link are far too long and complex to guess or brute force, so are you saying that they are leaked somewhere?\n\nThanks, and good luck with your future bug hunting.","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2016-04-26T22:09:56.666Z","updated_at":"2016-04-26T22:09:56.666Z","actor":{"username":"bugtriage-josh","cleared":false,"url":"/bugtriage-josh","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"/assets/avatars/default-71a302d706457f3d3a31eb30fa3e73e6cf0b1d677b8fa218eaeaffd67ae97918.png"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"uber","actor_is_team_member":false,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":929898,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::BugNew","message":"Hi Josh,\n\nFirst of all thanks for the update and i agree with you on this that id used in the issue are too complex too guess which makes brute forcing very difficult.\nAnd yes there is possibility of information leakage below mentioned scenarios helped in the information leakage of ids\n\nPossible attacking scenario here would be :\n\nScenario one \n\n1:Victim logged in application, for his/her ease to go back to same functionality, copied the subscription link\n\n2:At the same time he might be chatting with someone \n\n3:There might be a possibility that he mistakenly shares that url on chat with other person \n\n\nScenario two \n\n1:If victim is in cyber cafe and gets logged out of the application(uber) from his/her system then attacker comes on the same system and able to fetch through the browser history (since no authorization check is present on the same url)\n\n\n-For more clarification i have attached screenshots related  screnario two\n\n\n2:Since the IDs  are sensitive information (i.e. related to authenticated user)are travelling and getting revealed in url\n\n-my suggestion any user specific sensitive information should travel in the parameters of the body of request \u0026 not in url of the application","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2016-04-27T07:55:39.495Z","updated_at":"2016-04-27T07:55:39.495Z","actor":{"username":"sadhu16","cleared":false,"url":"/sadhu16","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/070/036/0d038cea418ac972b0f0410481381c1a11610436_original.jpg/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"attachments":[{"id":89790,"filename":"uber-Subscription_url_fetched_from_history-27.04.16.png","type":"image/png","url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/089/790/0f63a706faa262d49d6d02861561e0c8c62f76d5/uber-Subscription_url_fetched_from_history-27.04.16.png?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22uber-Subscription_url_fetched_from_history-27.04.16.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27uber-Subscription_url_fetched_from_history-27.04.16.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQRCOM766B%2F20211011%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20211011T133840Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEHUaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQC2plSLprTu8RjGD8JYtZWBPt0cszlQG9FE345fmJX2hAIhALFlvJYKDzrEhN7%2FvlACW3w%2FuqitMoDByli%2BB32UD4xHKoMECO7%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQAhoMMDEzNjE5Mjc0ODQ5Igydotw%2BzjeVoEUzifsq1wO17iYJRnZ0fDCk2qA3GFkCAi2TACWamwiykehERisJcA6JAf5%2BKDXCSCA9Z5sJN1RS6yYikkzrd1g0%2FNHQvlKNEb%2F0bkFdpBo983pYtuPm%2FjZwdUmgycUkQTsKElvIdrra2ORU8syHUfTSsU0jkhKy1nTU1EUbOyVSpNZUO9kXRRe3ohujd32sjmj8LzGUv8aTvRQduIzkPVeEQOKzFH7EgJMvdNR3vaK2TDhSXjMkBaQKBFqnh6PEMyOLZDUpbrlIy%2BoEq2r%2B%2F10hoGkdsLCXXLTZ6FqEIiLpzSb0Iu7CYkr0MdHXUykD4DOTntKsy9rifi4r4BROm%2BFSV7DvWqgt3W4BdQyDDpqk1mezBTFX0MzxjgcpwKW8P9MAJbLCDmqfTTPFk4Q3hwN16